High-level overview
- Goal: Generate {MASK_WORD} reviews for businesses across categories (restaurants, salons, auto shops, hotels, etc.) with adjustable tone, length, and platform style (Google, Yelp, Facebook).
- Inputs:
  - Business profile: name, category, location, specialties, notable features, hours, price range.
  - Customer persona: name, visit context, expertise level, preferences, sentiment (1–5 stars), tone (casual, professional, enthusiastic, concise), language/locale.
