- Safeguards:
  - Avoid false claims or unverifiable specifics.
  - No defamatory content, hate speech, personal data, or impersonation.
  - Clearly synthetic content; include an option to tag as “generated sample” to comply with platform policies and local laws.

Data model
- BusinessProfile
